I'm having exactly the same issue, all tables I define in XSL-FO are not rendered in the PDF.

XSL-FO Below result in an entirely blank PDF:

&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt;
&lt;fo:root xmlns:fo=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format&quot;&gt;
	&lt;fo:layout-master-set&gt;
		&lt;fo:simple-page-master master-name=&quot;simple&quot; 
					page-height=&quot;29.7cm&quot; page-width=&quot;210mm&quot;
					margin-top=&quot;1cm&quot; margin-bottom=&quot;2cm&quot; margin-left=&quot;2cm&quot; margin-right=&quot;2cm&quot;&gt;
			&lt;fo:region-body margin-top=&quot;0cm&quot;/&gt;
			&lt;fo:region-before extent=&quot;1.5cm&quot;/&gt;
			&lt;fo:region-after extent=&quot;1.5cm&quot;/&gt;
		&lt;/fo:simple-page-master&gt;
	&lt;/fo:layout-master-set&gt;
	&lt;fo:page-sequence master-reference=&quot;simple&quot;&gt;
		&lt;fo:flow flow-name=&quot;xsl-region-body&quot;&gt;
			&lt;fo:block&gt;
				&lt;fo:table border=&quot;0.5pt solid black&quot; text-align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;
						&lt;fo:table-body&gt;
							&lt;fo:table-row&gt;
								&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid black&quot;&gt;
									&lt;fo:block&gt; upper left &lt;/fo:block&gt;
								&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;
								&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid black&quot;&gt;
									&lt;fo:block&gt; upper right &lt;/fo:block&gt;
								&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;
							&lt;/fo:table-row&gt;
							&lt;fo:table-row&gt;
								&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid black&quot;&gt;
									&lt;fo:block&gt; lower left &lt;/fo:block&gt;
								&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;
								&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid black&quot;&gt;
									&lt;fo:block&gt; lower right &lt;/fo:block&gt;
								&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;
							&lt;/fo:table-row&gt;
						&lt;/fo:table-body&gt;
					&lt;/fo:table&gt;
				&lt;/fo:block&gt;
		&lt;/fo:flow&gt;
	&lt;/fo:page-sequence&gt;
&lt;/fo:root&gt;

Found the solution, table has to have three key properties; 

1. table-layout=&quot;fixed&quot;.

2. fo:table-column with width defined for each column.

3. each table-cell padding must be defined.

Working version below;

&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;utf-8&quot;?&gt; 
&lt;fo:root xmlns:fo=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Format&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:layout-master-set&gt;  
&lt;fo:simple-page-master master-name=&quot;simple&quot; page-height=&quot;29.7cm&quot; page-width=&quot;210mm&quot; margin-top=&quot;1cm&quot; margin-bottom=&quot;2cm&quot; margin-left=&quot;2cm&quot; margin-right=&quot;2cm&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:region-body margin-top=&quot;0cm&quot;/&gt;  
&lt;fo:region-before extent=&quot;1.5cm&quot;/&gt;  
&lt;fo:region-after extent=&quot;1.5cm&quot;/&gt;  
&lt;/fo:simple-page-master&gt;  
&lt;/fo:layout-master-set&gt;  
&lt;fo:page-sequence master-reference=&quot;simple&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:flow flow-name=&quot;xsl-region-body&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:block&gt;  
&lt;fo:table table-layout=&quot;fixed&quot; border=&quot;0.0pt solid black&quot; text-align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:table-column column-width=&quot;50mm&quot;/&gt;
&lt;fo:table-column column-width=&quot;50mm&quot;/&gt;
&lt;fo:table-body&gt;  
&lt;fo:table-row&gt;  
&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid #dddddd&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:block&gt; upper left &lt;/fo:block&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;  
&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid #dddddd&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:block&gt; upper right &lt;/fo:block&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table-row&gt;  
&lt;fo:table-row&gt;  
&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid #dddddd&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:block&gt; lower left &lt;/fo:block&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;  
&lt;fo:table-cell padding=&quot;6pt&quot; border=&quot;0.5pt solid #dddddd&quot;&gt;  
&lt;fo:block&gt; lower right &lt;/fo:block&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table-cell&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table-row&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table-body&gt;  
&lt;/fo:table&gt;  
&lt;/fo:block&gt;  
&lt;/fo:flow&gt;  
&lt;/fo:page-sequence&gt; 
&lt;/fo:root&gt;
